reviews.review_text:
Kickin' Ass Right, Left & Centre This the kind of show we left home for!

Rockin from first to last - do yourself a treat and settle into this one!  Smokin' Shakedown, Music, Rider & Terrapin - what more do you want!

and this recording matrix is the best of all those available here.

I encourage you to treat yourself to the hotness that is this how.

BTW Phil ROckS through this show check it out!

Gary B., Vancouver Island, BC
